+ - `run-cyspbot-deploy-update`: runs on `workflow_dispatch`, or on `workflow_run` after the `ci` workflow completes successfully on `main`; it runs `chikachow/cyspbot-deploy`'s `update-cyspbot.yml` workflow on `main`.
+
